general.desc: DISA Ltd is an investment holding company. The company's operating segments are Technology and Investment holding. It generates maximum revenue from the Technology segment. Geographically, it derives a majority of revenue from Hong Kong and also has a presence in Singapore; United States, and the People's Republic of China.
general.short_desc: DISA Ltd through its subsidiaries is engaged in e-waste business. Its business segments are Energy Management Services, Supply of construction materials, Technology and Investment holding.
